OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunshine this evening as most showers
OL,7,Fdie out. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be mainy dry with clear spells.
OL,9,FChance of a ground frost across the
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mainly dry, bright morning.
OL,13,FCloud will bubble up through the day
OL,14,Fto give a few afternoon showers
OL,15,Finland, while the east coast will be
OL,16,Flargely sunny.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
