OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,6,For showers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,7,Foccasionally heavy at first. Drier on
OL,8,FThursday. Milder than of late,
OL,9,Fpotentially warm in brighter spells.
